Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.69,0:01:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one is pushed into a corner during a Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what is it they need more than anything to press on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is one's own strong will and determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duelist lacking this courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.37,0:01:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will only end up betraying themselves\Nand their friend's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so I still want to protect my friends!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect Yugi!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Lightning Arrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady is beaten!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use these to save your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.81,0:01:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Duel with your will and determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.78,0:02:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a Duelist.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that right, my other self?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rescue Mokuba!\N Kaiba VS Pegasus"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're finally here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus' castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You{\i0} guys...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You earned enough Star Chips?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only three can now enter as finalists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are those three people!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.32,0:02:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've met all the conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:44.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There shouldn't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it into the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.85,0:03:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't allowed to enter this castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Come to think of it, how did you even get on the island--\N-Don't be so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let this pass~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.75,0:03:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-l-e-a-s-e~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.86,0:03:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I {\i1}can't{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow them all to--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's {\i1}that{\i0} feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you bastards! Open up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:40.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Grandpa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will rescue you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.29,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit Keith!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi oi, ain't this a surprise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you got out of that cave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandit Keith...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the nerve to trap us in a cave!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get all pissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be your opponent later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An interestin' show's about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba and Pegasus' Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun and Pegasus' Duel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.20,0:04:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The four contestants in the championship tournament...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Pegasus' Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it seems like some uninvited guests have let themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll let it slide this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, a special performance has been prepared for the ones who have survived their matches in Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To show his appreciation of your entering this tournament, Master Pegasus has prepared a special match for our guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will all simply participate as observants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just wants to show us how strong he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well now, that may be the case indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking down on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, take your time and enjoy watching this special match.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll surely beat Pegasus and bring you back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome! Welcome to my castle\N once again, Kaiba boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.93,0:05:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for the day where I could battle a proud Duelist such as yourself right here in my Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry one bit, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply defeat me in this Duel,\Nand I'll return Mokuba boy to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.65,0:06:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's enjoy a great Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus' power comes from his Millennium Eye,\Nthe power to see into minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like Kaiba and Pegasus to both lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if Pegasus loses, we won't be able to enter into the championship finals...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so let's hope to see {\i1}Kaiba{\i0} as the loser dog this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know in order to save\N Grandpa I have to beat Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, then why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.59,0:06:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want Kaiba-kun to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want him to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that the four official finalists have gathered in my castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found a way into the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expected no less from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It seems you as well, Yugi boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:06:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}share the same fate of fighting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.38,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's begin our Duel, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.18,0:07:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fighting you with these Duel Disks in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it supposed to be used as a fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it {\i1}is{\i0} a bit heavy for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.74,0:07:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you toss it around like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.64,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.78,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll allow the use of the Duel Disks, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have someone operate it in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.61,0:07:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, he will be following the memo I hand him for the cards he chooses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will not change the fact that I am your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus, you bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me one on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.81,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is basic gaming strategy to never fight on your enemy's turf...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mind games have already begun, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, this little trick of yours will hold no advantage over my Millennium Eye anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring out the person who will operate the Duel Disk for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks a bit strange, doesn't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did Pegasus do to Mokuba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Kaiba boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad to have\N Mokuba boy as your opponent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.01,0:08:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba boy's soul has been sealed in this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sealed in the card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he mean by that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he's been hypnotized, oi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mokuba boy in front of you is merely a soulless shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.48,0:09:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he will respond to simple orders I give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy, if you can defeat me
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will release Mokuba boy's\N soul from the sealed card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus' Power of Darkness has sealed Mokuba-kun too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-kun did such reckless things\Nin order to save Mokuba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you will operate the Duel Disk for me, Mokuba-boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's the {\i1}matter{\i0}, Kaiba boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you wanted, we'll be using the Duel Disks in our Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.31,0:10:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A-are you telling me to fight against Mokuba...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the one thing...\N that's the one thing I can't do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.71,0:10:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand, Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.44,0:10:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take back using the Duel Disks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.01,0:10:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your cherished big brother unfortunately\Ndoes not wish to fight against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's prepare to Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a Duel Ring... all the way up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:10:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally it begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba-kun and Pegasus' Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will play by the "Kingdom Rules".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please prepare your Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:12:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun! Watch out for\N Pegasus' Dragon-Type Sealing Jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon-Type Sealing Jar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.51,0:12:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against this jar, even Blue-Eyes White Dragon is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose your cards carefully, Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Why are you giving Kaiba advice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.11,0:12:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Kaiba is fighting to get back\Nhis precious Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't lose no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I'll take your feelings into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I trust in my cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish... wasting others' advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter who the opponent...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will fight alongside my Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll {\i1}defeat{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll take my turn first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I will set another card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it a Magic Card... or a Trap Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.91,0:13:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I already have a Blue-Eyes in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can use it and open with an all-out strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the problem is whether he has that Dragon-Type Sealing card Yugi told me about...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one card face-down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also... Rude Kaiser in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack the Defense monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OH NOOO~!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.34,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy's monster has\N 1800 Attack Points, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.91,0:14:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That exceeds my monster's Defense Points by 200...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This card may work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parrot Dragon, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will activate a Counter-Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I had set is Hypnotism!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.08,0:14:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card reduces the Attack of your monster by 800 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance, Rude Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh nooo~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you taking this seriously, Pegasus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:14:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus is pretty weak, ain't he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak he couldn't counter anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...! That Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.01,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Pegasus' way of messing with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Kaiba-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'd say it's about time to end the\Nentertaining tension I've filled the air with, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba boy, I can read your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And of course, that includes your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the progress I've made in the turns so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's a high possibility he doesn't have the Dragon-Type Sealing Jar in his hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My instinct tells me he {\b1}doesn't{\b0} have the Dragon Capture Jar in his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.79,0:15:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, I'll end this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there. Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.09,0:15:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't show me that card.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to activate a Trap Card against the card you're about to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.13,0:16:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I played face-down was the Prophesy card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card's effect allows me to guess the Attack Points of a monster in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess if it's "Big or small".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I guess right, that card becomes mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.16,0:16:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I predict it has more than 2000 Attack Points, big!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that is not enough to prove this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll predict further details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card has 3000 Attack Points, and it is your most trusted card.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Pegasus see my hand somehow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.26,0:16:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, this card is now mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's it feel, Kaiba boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.83,0:17:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your most trusted card being stolen, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun's Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.59,0:17:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As I thought... Is Pegasus really reading Kaiba-kun's mind with his Millennium Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe he actually had a Trap Card waiting to take the opponent's card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now add this card to my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let us continue with the Duel, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.59,0:17:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn I'll just switch Rude Kaiser to Defense Mode, and it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.06,0:17:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll pay you back next turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.90,0:17:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It looks like you've got something planned on that face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.81,0:17:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know everything in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mind Scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have a Virus Card in your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You plan to use the dark clown to activate the Virus Combo...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.43,0:18:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and destroying my deck with this deadly infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.69,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Indeed this is a clever plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it won't work against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.46,0:18:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play a set card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'll play a monster in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with that my turn is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus! This turn you're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My card is the Death Virus Combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.76,0:18:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll offer Saggi the Dark Clown to activate the Virus Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To destroy your entire deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, go ahead and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saggi the Dark Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.54,0:18:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Virus Combo that caused Yugi to suffer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.14,0:18:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this move works, Pegasus is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus saw through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll activate my face-down Magic Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:18:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card doubles the Attack Points of all Dark Attribute Monsters in play!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saggi the Dark Clown has a Dark Attribute...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore its Attack is doubled!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not good...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Virus card only works with monsters under 1000 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Virus Card has been stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.44,0:19:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He even saw through my Virus Card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.25,0:19:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place my card, Dark Rabbit, in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it is a Dark Attribute Monster, its Attack doubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Rabbit, attack Saggi the Dark Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.61,0:19:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Virus Combo that gave Yugi so much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was defeated so easily...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba boy.... the fear is beginning to cloud your mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But.... it's just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will experience true terror when you enter my world...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(141,141)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, Pegasus' trump card, Toon World, appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus' Toons are dodging every one of Kaiba-kun's attacks and transforming them into Toons.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.05,0:20:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even turns the Blue-Eyes into a Toon to make Kaiba-kun suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, even if you're the one who invented Duel Monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dirty for you to own this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: {\c&HFFFFFF&}"Kaiba Falls! The Invincible Toon World"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel Standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
